            "sentence_md5": "6db868ddcb9a8cd3eb8d99bea9e4b88f",
            "sentance": "“The concept of cheating is based on the false assumption that the system is legitimate and there is something wrong with the individual who’s doing it,” he said, “That’s too easy an answer.",
            "phonetic": "/ðə ˈkɒnsept ɒv ˈtʃiːtɪŋ ɪz beɪst ɒn ðə fɔːls əˈsʌmpʃn ðæt ðə ˈsɪstəm ɪz lɪˈdʒɪtɪmət ænd ðeə(r) ɪz ˈsʌmθɪŋ rɒŋ wɪð ði ˌɪndɪˈvɪdʒuəl huːz ˈduːɪŋ ɪt, hi sed, ðæts tuː ˈiːzi ən ˈɑːnsə(r)./",
            "translation": "他说：“作弊的概念是基于这样一种错误的假设：体制是合法的，而做这件事的个人有问题，这是一个太过于简单的答案。”",
            "audio_file": "data/audio/6db868ddcb9a8cd3eb8d99bea9e4b88f.mp3",
            "analysis": {
